###Code Repository
A kind of Gitbuh but decentralised. Rewards based on commits.

###Security Cameras 
Use case: you can install security cameras in a kindergarten but no-one can access the footage unless 51% of parents give the consent to do it. It would solve the privacy vs security issue.

###Plugin as Coinpayments
But open, as with myetherwallet, you can add custom token just defining name, address and decimals

###Call-Center / Customer-Care on demand
Uber economy; Decentralised customer care on demand.
It would be also possible to create services for marketplaces (i.e. themeforest) where support is based on some reward system

###Products Warranty / delivery tracking / dropshipping infrastructure
bill/warranty/tracking on the blockchain (QRcode)
You could also make automated order  fulfillment with smart-contracts for dropshipping services

###Turnover
Shifts system. I.e. a Netflix licens give me the right to use up to 4 devices but we could pay it in 20 people and use it according to a shared calendar.

###Easy Mobile Investments
Every day we send users a push notification e they can decide whether to invest 10, 20, 50 o 100 $ in just a click.
It’s in between betting and investing: instead of betting on Lotto or football, users can quick invest on crypto

###Satellites as a service
Platform where users can buy services based on a satellite infrastructure.
Various applications (i.e. security, urban planning, architecture etc)
There’s some company that makes commercial satellites. I have a contact.
https://vimeo.com/161656838

###Coupon
Tool that allows users to easily create Smart Contracts that can be transferable, time-based e non-cumulative

###Collecting points card
Similar to ENJIN COIN but in this case you can also collect points from supermarket, fly-miliage,  petrol station discounts etc.)

###Private Photo Album
Save and privately share a beautiful, private collection of photos, videos and thoughts of your children that you and your family will always cherish. Same model as 23snaps but on the blockchain.

###Post Mortem Message
Wikileaks Style, you can release a message triggered by specified conditions: i.e the death of the author.

###Package Manager Crypto
Same model of  Mnp javascript.

###E-sports Betting
There’s not much to explain.

###Widget con contenuti originali
Most of online publishers today are using widget like this https://www.taboola.com/
They give additional content and ads usually placed at the end of the main article as related or promoted. Usually mediocre quality of contents.
The proposal is to create a platform for author that can create and monetise on quality content distributed through a widget for online newspapers, magazines and blogs.

###Usage Rights Contracts
A usage right contract is usually not so precise or expensive because it has to be written and registered by a lawyer. In this plaftorm authors and agencies can interact and write smart contracts where to define terms and condition of usage of a specific creative work.

###Custom Insurance
Crypto wallet are not guaranteed or insured and this usually scares most of the people
On the go insurance i.e for silicon tits during a flight
Insurance for your laptop in case of theft

###Scholarship / Patent
Researchers can apply with their projects and privates investors can invest on that specific research.

###Mining as business model.
Instead of advertising or subscription for online services.

###ICO VCs
Una piattaforma per ico pensata per VCs, dove due diligence, vesting, expenses reports vengono enforced dalla piattaforma. Tutte le ico vengono operate tramite il token della piattaforma. Con un sistema di master node fatto Vc, proof-of-diligence. Potrebbe essere la long term vision dell'hedge fund. Poi ci colleghiamo pure il GitHub/npm/freelancing platform.

###Basic Income
Token legato ad un valore nel mondo reale. Utilizzo di tecniche come inflazione. Legare basic income a identità univoca. Retorica accelerazionismo: Automatizzare il lavoro e dare redditi alle persone.
